title: Action City - Urban Retro Music Pack
description: Brace yourself for Action City - 15 action packed tracks from Wob Wob Rob!
longDescription:
Action City is a collection of tracks that pay homage to the classic games of the 90's (think Toejam & Earl, Double Dragon, Megaman, and more). Whether you need a funky anthem, a groovy chase song or a rocking boss battle theme, Action City has it all. Don’t miss this chance to spice up your action-packed creation!


Listen to the sampler - Action City - Urban Retro Music Pack (youtube.com)


Action City contains 15 looping music tracks and 2 stingers:


LOOPS

  • Blaze City (1:44)
  • Swagger Street (1:25)
  • Crazy Crossing (1:04)
  • Backstreet Beatdown (1:13)
  • Rumbletown (1:38)
  • Fuzzville (1:07)
  • Stop! Go! (1:04)
  • Battle Bus (1:08)
  • Jam Alley (1:14)
  • All Mapped Out (1:04) 
  • Power Plaza (1:45) 
  • Creepy Courtyard (1:36) 
  • Bonus Boulevard (0.33)
  • Turbo Tunnel (1:32) 
  • Fond Farewell (1:04)


STINGERS

  • Level Complete (0:04)
  • Level Fail (0:04)
